Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这都过了差不多一年了\N{\fs38}But I-it's been like a whole year!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是六个小时\N{\fs38}It's been six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦里的时间是现实时间的一百分之一\N{\fs38}Dreams move one one-hundredth the speed of reality, and dog
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而狗的时间是人的七分之一\N{\fs38}Time is one-seventh human time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里过一天 外面一分钟\N{\fs38}So, you know, every day here is like a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和<盗梦空间>一样 把人搞得很晕 而且很蠢\N{\fs38}It's like "Inception," Morty, so if it's confusing and stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这部人人爱的电影就这个样\N{\fs38}then so is everyone's favorite movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我很喜欢这样的生活呀\N{\fs38}Aw, man. I really liked this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过至少我没有真的拉在裤子里吧\N{\fs38}Well, at least I didn't really crap my pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这事儿是真的 在你睡着之前就拉了\N{\fs38}No, no, that happened before you went to sleep, Morty.
