Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一一件确确实实发生了的事\N{\fs38}Out of all the things that happened to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你拉在裤子里了\N{\fs38} that was the only real thing that, you know, is that you crapped your pants.
