Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有些沾到我手上了\N{\fs38}I got some on my hands, Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我给弄到梦境植入器上了 还有一坨掉进了我的嘴里\N{\fs38}And then I got it on the dream inceptor, and a piece fell in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 不是吧\N{\fs38}Aw, man, geez! Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了 Morty\N{\fs38}Look, d-d-d-don't worry about it, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来把这个吃了\N{\fs38}Here, here take these, Morty. Take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些药能让我醒过来还是怎么的\N{\fs38}Are these pills supposed to wake me up, or something?
