Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了我们的计划 Morty\N{\fs38}It's necessary for the plan, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 哥们儿\N{\fs38}Don't even trip, dawg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况很糟 雪球陛下\N{\fs38}It's pretty bad, Emperor Snowball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还需要做一次手术\N{\fs38}We're gonna need to do another operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜一切\N{\fs38}Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜一切代价救回我的宝贝Morty \N{\fs38}Anything for my precious Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为您的会计师 我必须告诉您\N{\fs38}Sir, as your accountant, I must advise you that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些医疗支出会让您的财政到达岌岌可危的地步\N{\fs38}these medical expenses are putting you in serious financial jeopardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您可能会失去您的帝国\N{\fs38}You could lose your kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去他的帝国 斤斤计较的会计\N{\fs38}To hell with my kingdom, bean counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意牺牲这一切 来换得这个人类的健康和幸福\N{\fs38}I would trade it all for my human's health and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他们会为我们做到这一步吗\N{\fs38}Do you think they would have done this for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又不是他们\N{\fs38}We are not them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是 他们\N{\fs38}We are not... them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集军队\N{\fs38}Assemble the troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了一个决定\N{\fs38}I've made a decision.
