Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会造成更多的残忍与伤痛\N{\fs38}will lead to nothing but more heartbreak, more cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们决定去新世界建立一个智慧狗类的社会\N{\fs38}Instead, we will go to a new world and colonize it with a society of intelligent dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会再犯人类的错误\N{\fs38}One that will not make the same mistakes as humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且会有强制宠物保险\N{\fs38}and one where pet insurance will be mandatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想你的 雪球\N{\fs38}I'm gonna miss you, Snowball.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以叫我嗅嗅 Morty\N{\fs38}You can call me Snuffles, Morty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会想你的 非常想念\N{\fs38}and I'm going to miss you, too, very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry\N{\fs38}Jerry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs38}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和<老黄狗>的结局一样\N{\fs38}It's just like the end of "Old Yeller."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么说是因为里面也有狗吧\N{\fs38}Oh, Jerry. You mean because it had dogs in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个智慧狗类居住的世界\N{\fs38}Wow! A whole world populated by intelligent dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想知道会是什么样啊 Rick\N{\fs38}I wonder what it'll be like, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得肯定很棒 Morty\N{\fs38}I think it will be great, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以发展成一个\N{\fs38}You know, it's g I-I-I-I-it could be developed in-into
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好的全年龄向节目啊\N{\fs38}a very satisfying project for people of all ages.
