Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个想法很令人欣慰啊 Rick\N{\fs38}You know, that's a real comforting idea, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道什么呢 Morty\N{\fs38}What do you know, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又知道啥呢\N{\fs38}What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 大家好\N{\fs38}Hi, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你们恐怖课的新老师\N{\fs38}I'm your new teacher for scary class.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫恐怖Johnson\N{\fs38}My name is Scary Mr. Johnson.
