Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我爸的名字 你们干脆叫我恐怖Glenn好了\N{\fs38}That's my dad's name, so why don't you just call me Scary Glenn, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你们之前的老师\N{\fs38}So, anyway, I understand your previous teacher
